responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "8FA3618E4FB3E0AF13A6AC82627EE67A", "It is an odd shard that has embedded itself into the crags of the Highwaymen Hills. Its use is limited, but its rarity promises to fetch much among the crafters and archaeologists. It is rather unfortunate that to claim your riches one must test the shark infested waters of Highwaymen Hills. The Forsaken Blades will not just let you into their nest.")
